auto lo
iface lo net loopback

# IPV4 Configuration

auto enp0s31f6

iface enp0s31f6 inet static
    address            192.168.1.30
    gateway            192.168.1.254
    broadcast          192.168.1.255
    netmask            255.255.255.0
    dns-nameservers    8.8.8.8 8.8.4.4


